@startuml
title BidMart Component Diagram - core-be Bidding (Individual: Muhamad Hakim Nizami)
left to right direction
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

actor "core-fe\nCore Frontend" as CoreFE <<Container>>

package "core-be Container\nRust Axum REST API" {

  package "Infrastructure Layer" {
    component "BidController\nPOST /auctions/{id}/bids\nGET  /auctions/{id}/bids\nGET  /auctions/{id}" as BidController <<Controller>>
    component "BidWebSocketHandler\nGET /auctions/{id}/stream" as BidWS <<Controller>>
    component "SqlxAuctionRepository" as AuctionRepo <<Repository>>
    component "SqlxBidRepository" as BidRepo <<Repository>>
    component "InternalWalletClient\ncalls auth-be wallet API" as WalletClient <<Adapter>>
    component "TokioBidBroadcaster\nin-process pub/sub" as Broadcaster <<Adapter>>
    component "SystemClock" as Clock <<Service>>
  }

  package "Application Layer" {
    component "PlaceBidUseCase" as PlaceBidUC <<UseCase>>
    component "ListBidsUseCase" as ListBidsUC <<UseCase>>
    component "GetAuctionWithBidsUseCase" as GetAuctionUC <<UseCase>>
  }

  package "Domain Layer" {
    component "Bid\nentity" as BidEntity <<Domain>>
    component "Auction\nentity, state machine" as AuctionEntity <<Domain>>
    component "BidAmount, BidIncrement\nvalue objects" as BidValue <<Domain>>
    component "BidError\nNotHighest, AuctionClosed,\nSelfBid, BelowMinIncrement,\nInsufficientFunds" as BidError <<Domain>>
    interface "AuctionRepository" as AuctionRepoTrait <<Trait>>
    interface "BidRepository" as BidRepoTrait <<Trait>>
    interface "WalletGateway" as WalletTrait <<Trait>>
    interface "BidBroadcaster" as BroadcasterTrait <<Trait>>
  }
}

database "core-db\nauctions, bids,\nlistings, orders" as CoreDB <<Database>>
component "auth-be\nWallet API" as AuthBE <<External Service>>

CoreFE --> BidController : REST place bid /\nlist bids
CoreFE --> BidWS : WebSocket subscribe\nlive bid stream

BidController --> PlaceBidUC : invokes
BidController --> ListBidsUC : invokes
BidController --> GetAuctionUC : invokes
BidWS --> Broadcaster : subscribe

PlaceBidUC --> AuctionRepoTrait
PlaceBidUC --> BidRepoTrait
PlaceBidUC --> WalletTrait
PlaceBidUC --> BroadcasterTrait
PlaceBidUC --> Clock
ListBidsUC --> BidRepoTrait
GetAuctionUC --> AuctionRepoTrait
GetAuctionUC --> BidRepoTrait

PlaceBidUC ..> BidEntity : creates
PlaceBidUC ..> AuctionEntity : loads, validates
PlaceBidUC ..> BidValue : uses
PlaceBidUC ..> BidError : returns

AuctionRepo ..|> AuctionRepoTrait
BidRepo ..|> BidRepoTrait
WalletClient ..|> WalletTrait
Broadcaster ..|> BroadcasterTrait

AuctionRepo --> CoreDB : SELECT FOR UPDATE auction\nUPDATE current_highest
BidRepo --> CoreDB : INSERT bid\nSELECT bids by auction
WalletClient --> AuthBE : reserve / release funds

note bottom of PlaceBidUC
Transactional flow:
1. Lock auction row
2. Validate state, amount, increment
3. Reserve buyer funds via wallet
4. Insert bid, update auction
5. Broadcast new highest bid
end note
@enduml
